
sample_ffdh: Show how to use FFDH API

To run (load and start) container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 run sample_ffdh.img

To send data to container and run with predefined keys:
$ echo s >  testfile
$ cmtest data -f100 testfile

To send data to container and run with generate private and public keys:
$ echo g >  testfile
$ cmtest data -f100 testfile

To unload container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 unload
